The pilot held a private pilot certificate with airplane single-engine and multi-engine land 
ratings. He held a third-class airman medical certificate issued on April 28, 2014, with the 
limitation that he must have available glasses for near vision. At the time of his last medical 
exam, the pilot reported flight experience that included 1,860 total hours and 104 hours in the 
last 6 months.
